  "notes": [
    "This study compares GenMine TOP (dual DNA-RNA panel) with FoundationOne CDx (DNA-only panel) for sarcoma genomic profiling using real-world data from Japan's nationwide C-CAT database.",
    "The study included 1046 patients with sarcoma registered between August 2023 and October 2024.",
    "GenMine TOP demonstrated superior performance in detecting fusion genes, particularly important for translocation-related sarcomas.",
    "The tumor-normal matched design of GenMine TOP enabled detection of germline pathogenic variants, which is not possible with tumor-only panels."
  ]
